    @ControlType(value=javafx.scene.control.ListView.class)
@ControlInterfaces(value={List.class,org.jemmy.interfaces.Selectable.class,org.jemmy.interfaces.Scroll.class},
                   encapsulates={java.lang.Object.class,java.lang.Object.class})
public class ListViewWrap<CONTROL extends javafx.scene.control.ListView>
extends NodeWrap<CONTROL>
implements org.jemmy.interfaces.Scroll, org.jemmy.interfaces.Selectable<java.lang.Object>
    List support in JemmyFX is provided through a few different control interfaces. Namely, these are List, Parent and Selectable.
    Author:
    shura, Alexander Kouznetsov
